<table><tr><td class="bullet"></td><td class="bullet">&#149;</td>
<td class="para">This is not a complete list of side effects and others may occur. Call your doctor for medical advice about side effects. You may report side effects to FDA at 1-800-FDA-1088.</td></tr></table>

<p><br /></p><table><tr><td class="para"><strong>What other drugs will affect eyebright?</strong></td></tr></table>

<table><tr><td class="bullet"></td><td class="bullet">&#149;</td>
<td class="para">Interactions between eyebright and other prescription or over-the-counter medicines or herbal/health supplements have not been reported.  Talk to your doctor, pharmacist, or health care professional before taking eyebright if you are taking any other medicines or supplements.</td></tr></table>

<p><br /></p><table><tr><td class="para"><strong>Where can I get more information?</strong></td></tr></table>

